704627f-b.text:
Glenmore Avenue, at the S. E. corner of Pennsylvania Avenue, showing a Russian Greek Orthodox Church. Views 2 and 3 show the rear of the church, looking north across subway construction, from Pitkin Avenue. Past the church is Public School No. 173.

September 13, 1940
Views 1, 2, 3

P. L. Sperr
